Package: cps
Title: Reproducible Continuous PD-L1 CPS Modeling in Advanced Gastric/GEJ Cancer (AGAMENON)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alberto", "Carmona-Bayonas",
           email = "alberto.carmonabayonas@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = "Medical Oncology Department, Hospital Universitario Morales Meseguer, Murcia, Spain"),
    person("AGAMENON-SEOM Investigators", role = "aut"))
Description: De-identified patient-level data and functions to reproduce the
    tables and figures of the AGAMENON analysis comparing dichotomized,
    non-overlapping interval and continuous (restricted cubic spline) modeling
    of the PD-L1 Combined Positive Score (CPS) for first-line immunotherapy in
    advanced gastric and gastroesophageal junction adenocarcinoma. The bundled
    dataset has the patient identifier removed so individuals are not traceable.
